Title: Silver Ring Round Cut with Sidestone CZ Engagement Sterling/925 Size 8 AW28
Description: STERLING I have for offer a sterling silver/925 Round Cut with Sidestone CZ Engagement ring size 8. The stone measures 7mm diameter. Otherwise, my system automatically leaves feedback when you leave it. Basically: My wife and I have made a life decision to sell the things that will allow us to better our future. We both have day jobs so if you ask any questions during that time, we may not be able to answer until that evening. If you are not happy, then we are not happy. Let us know and we will make it right. Payment is due in seven days.
